          "evidence_chunk_id": "chunk-4299634f8ecc46ae",
          "evidence_text_excerpt": "Competitive rates for clients who are buying their next home.\nWe offer competitive alternative rates for homeowners who are looking to buy their next property. Compare rates and reward your client\u2019s payment history.\nConnect with a BDM\nExclusive access.",
