          "evidence_text_excerpt": "03\nManage your clients\u2019 mortgages in the Broker Portal.\nWith full access to the Broker Portal, you can manage all your applications, track deal progress, and make the mortgage process smoother for your clients.\nWhat Mortgage Brokers think of Haventree Bank.\nTESTIMONIALS\nWhat our clients say about us\nTrustpilot\n\"Thanks for Punam,i really appreciate her for all the help she made for me today to explain everything regarding the changing our bi weekly payment she explained everything in details...\"\nevangelyn\nTrustpilot\n\"My experience was great due to the fact that the representative (Punam) ,was very professional, polite and extremely patient.\"\ntchester\nTrustpilot\n\"Rizell made my request easy to understand and simple . She walked me through every step and it only took a few minutes. Thank you\"\nMichael Pruitt\nTrustpilot\n\"Rizzel is really helpful and very detailed. I am happy that I was able",
