          "source_document_id": "src-haventree-html-0d26e0f4fbfe5d1c",
          "source_snapshot_id": "snap-ca0e76563ddbb38c",
          "evidence_chunk_id": "chunk-9228f69348512bbf",
          "evidence_text_excerpt": "nsed Mortgage Brokers. If you are ready to apply, your broker can connect with one of our Business Development Managers through the \u201c Connect with a BDM \u201d form on our broker page. If you\u2019re looking for a Mortgage Broker, you can use our Find a Broker tool to connect with a Mortgage Broker near you.\nDo you offer both fixed- and variable-rate mortgages?\nRight now, we offer fixed-rate mortgages only. We also have convertible mortgages \u2014 these start as short-term fixed-rate options that you can switch to a longer term later and take advantage of decreasing rate environments, without paying prepayment penalties.\nWhat is the minimum down payment required?\nWe require at least 20% down payment for a home purchase since we do not provide insured mortgage products. This approach helps us offer quicker approvals and more flexible options.\nWHAT\u2019S NEXT",
